description	"Wat Tambor

Class Summary:
A commander unit with special high-knockback concussion rifle.

Weapons:
- E-5 Blaster Rifle (3)
- Stouker Concussion Rifle (Secondary fire only)
- Frag Grenade (1)
- Tracking Darts (3)
- Poison Darts (3)

Inventory:
- Portable Sentry Gun
- Portable Shield

Attributes:
- Radar (Perma-sense 1)
- Hidden to sense
- Healing (2)
- Rally
- Bounty Hunter style getup and gun-kicks

Wat Tambor was a male Skakoan who was the foreman of the Techno Union and an executive of Baktoid Armor Workshop. During the Separatist Crisis, he pledged the Techno Union's resources to the Confederacy of Independent Systems, earning himself a seat on the Separatist Council during the Clone Wars."
